# definition Certificate

"**Certificate**" means the certificate of incorporation of Pied Piper, Inc. filed with the Secretary of State of the State of Delaware, as amended from time to time.

# definition Effective Time

"**Effective Time**" means the time at which the Certificate becomes effective under the DGCL.

# definition Founder Shares

"**Founder Shares**" means the six million (6,000,000) shares of common stock of the Company issued to the Founder at formation.
